These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, amber
The people have 2 different jobs:  scientist, teacher
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, pakistani
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, january
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, video-games
1. the pakistani is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
3. the scientist is in an even position##4
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Color   | yellow     | amber     |
| Job   | teacher     | scientist |
| Nationality   | nigerian | pakistani  |
| Birthday           | january    | august |
| Hobby         | video-games   | dancing       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, january
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, bellflower
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, bike
2 different pets are kept: dog, lizard
There 2 different types of food: corn, artichoke
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
2. the person driving the van is the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person driving the van is in an even position##4
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Birthday      | january    | december |
| Flower           | bellflower  | daffodil     |
| Transport   | bike       | van      |
| Pet           | dog        | lizard      |
| Food         | artichoke | corn     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, martial-arts
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, dressmaker
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, marigold
2 different games are played: bridge, monopoly
There are 2 different favourite colors: turquise, blood-red
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
2. the person who likes turquise is on the far left##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an odd position##4
4. the dressmaker is the person who likes blood-red##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Movie-Genre         | martial-arts     | animation    |
| Job           | doctor     | dressmaker |
| Flower   | marigold    | tulip   |
| Game         | bridge | monopoly   |
| Color     | turquise | blood-red |

