.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, kiwi
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, collecting
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, software-developer
House: farmhouse, palace
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the software-developer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |
| Food          | kiwi     | cranberry     |
| Hobby   | baking   | collecting        |
| Transport   | subway      | quad-bike         |
| Job   | software-developer | journalist       |
| House         | farmhouse  | palace |

