.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-5::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, december
The people have 2 different jobs:  pilot, teacher
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, indie
City: edinburgh, miami
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
2. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
3. the teacher is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Birthday          | december | february |
| Job           | pilot      | teacher     |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | r&b        |
| City   | edinburgh  | miami   |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate | cola   |

