.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-6::.
2 different games are played: billiard, monopoly
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, musician
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, montecristo
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, tulip
House: wooden, cottage
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4
2. the fisherman is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the person playing billiard is the fisherman##1
4. the musician is on the left of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Game      | monopoly        | billiard     |
| Job           | musician   | fisherman |
| Cigar   | montecristo     | davidoff    |
| Flower           | balloon-flower    | tulip    |
| House         | wooden | cottage   |

