There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, aquamarine
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, italian
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, family
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, trance
1. the person watching romance movies is in an even position##4
2. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
3. the fan of metal is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
4. the indonesian is the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Game         | snooker  | billiard |
| Color           | aquamarine   | lavender  |
| Nationality   | italian | indonesian  |
| Movie-Genre           | family     | romance      |
| Music-Genre     | trance    | metal      |

