3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| City          | hamburg | edinburgh       |
| Pet         | ferret | hamster |
| Color   | azure   | emerald       |
| Beverage   | almond-milk  | fanta  |
| Transport     | train   | bus        |

