The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, biathlon
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, thriller
1. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the thai##1
4. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |
| Nationality      | turkish    | thai         |
| Hobby           | rock-climbing | singing |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | blues       |
| Sport           | rugby     | biathlon  |
| Movie-Genre     | satire     | thriller         |

