.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, tea
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, purple
2 different games are played: canasta, snooker
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, thriller
City: hannover, london
1. the person watching thriller movies is the person who likes coral##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | tea      | milk     |
| Color   | purple    | coral  |
| Game           | canasta   | snooker |
| Movie-Genre         | crime | thriller |
| City     | hannover     | london     |

 